[emph]public function jsonGetModulesPermissionAction()[/emph]

Returns the project-module && user-role-project permissions.
This is a system functions and should not be re-writed.

[emph]public function jsonGetTranslatedStringsAction()[/emph]

Returns all the words translated in each modules for the request language.
This is a system functions and should not be re-writed.

[emph]public function jsonGetConfigurationsAction()[/emph]

Returns the front configurations from the configuration.ini (front.xxx),
and some others Core Settings.
This is a system functions and should not be re-written.
